Posts.Content: My friend works as an analyst in a clinical lab doing the paps. They receive so many samples its not unusual for the samples to get mixed up. Their lab has an error rate of 4 per 100. They are extremely careful with a redo second order. Like the others I was diagnosed with stage 3 cancer, never had another abnormal pap.
Posts.Title: Complex Cystic Mass & Breast Biopsy
